        	<div class="clear"></div>
        	<div class="post-info bebas">
        		<div class="parts">1 year ago&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        			|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Tags:
	        			
	        				<span class="tags"><a href="http://blog.viraptor.info/tagged/backup">backup</a></span>
	        			
	        				<span class="tags"><a href="http://blog.viraptor.info/tagged/linux">linux</a></span>
	        			
	        				<span class="tags"><a href="http://blog.viraptor.info/tagged/rsync">rsync</a></span>
	        			
	        				<span class="tags"><a href="http://blog.viraptor.info/tagged/rsnapshot">rsnapshot</a></span>
	        			
	        			&nbsp;
        			
        		
        		|&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Notes: <a href="http://blog.viraptor.info/post/51516551067/constructing-a-linux-home-backup-system#notes">5</a></div>
